{"id":50341,"date":"2026-03-31T15:36:58","date_gmt":"2026-03-31T14:36:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.portugalrunning.com\/eventos\/corrida-4-estacoes-primavera\/"},"modified":"2026-05-17T18:50:47","modified_gmt":"2026-05-17T17:50:47","slug":"corrida-4-estacoes-primavera","status":"publish","type":"ajde_events","link":"https:\/\/www.portugalrunning.com\/eventos\/corrida-4-estacoes-primavera\/","title":{"rendered":"Corrida 4 Esta\u00e7\u00f5es Primavera 2026"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<!-- Contentor Principal com T\u00edtulo -->\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; width: 100%; max-width: 1100px; margin: 20px auto;\">\n  \n  <!-- T\u00edtulo Principal -->\n  <h2 style=\"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 15px; border-left: 5px solid #06b6d4; padding-left: 15px;\">\n    Resultados\n  <\/h2>\n\n  <!-- Bloco do Iframe -->\n  <div style=\"border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\">\n    \n    <!-- Cabe\u00e7alho de Controlo -->\n    <div style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a; padding: 15px 20px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px;\">\n      <div>\n        <span style=\"background: #06b6d4; color: #fff; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;\">Live Scores<\/span>\n        <h3 style=\"margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.5px;\">GoinOnline &#8211; Resultados em Direto<\/h3>\n      <\/div>\n      \n      <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 10px;\">\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/goinonline.pt\/home\/scores\/6658b104b37c7f43b369c6bcc75f82df0efd2c2197316a34d0\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: #3b82f6; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; transition: all 0.2s ease; border: 1px solid #2563eb;\" rel=\"noopener\">\n           Abrir em Ecr\u00e3 Total \u2197\n        <\/a>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <!-- Zona do Iframe -->\n    <div style=\"width: 100%; height: 800px; background-color: #fff; position: relative;\">\n      <iframe \n        src=\"https:\/\/goinonline.pt\/home\/scores\/6658b104b37c7f43b369c6bcc75f82df0efd2c2197316a34d0\" \n        width=\"100%\" \n        height=\"100%\" \n        frameborder=\"0\"\n        style=\"display: block;\"\n        allow=\"clipboard-write\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        title=\"Resultados GoinOnline\">\n      <\/iframe>\n    <\/div>\n    \n    <!-- Rodap\u00e9 Info -->\n    <div style=\"background: #f8fafc; padding: 10px 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #64748b;\">Plataforma: <strong>GoinOnline<\/strong><\/span>\n      <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8;\">Atualiza\u00e7\u00e3o em tempo real<\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>A <strong>Corrida 4 Esta\u00e7\u00f5es Primavera 2026<\/strong> realiza-se na vila de Avelar, concelho de Ansi\u00e3o, assinalando o in\u00edcio do ciclo sazonal de competi\u00e7\u00f5es de estrada. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\ud83d\udccb <strong>Dados T\u00e9cnicos:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Nome:<\/strong> Corrida 4 Esta\u00e7\u00f5es \u2013 Etapa Primavera 2026. <\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Data:<\/strong> 17 de Maio de 2026<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Local:<\/strong> Vila de Avelar, Ansi\u00e3o (Distrito de Leiria). <\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Terreno\/Dist\u00e2ncias:<\/strong> Asfalto (Circuito Urbano) \/ 10 km (Prova Principal) e 5 km (Caminhada). <\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"p-rc_7b973435a30974ca-25\">\u2b50 <strong>Diferenciador:<\/strong> A etapa de Avelar caracteriza-se por um percurso urbano de altimetria moderada, atravessando o n\u00facleo hist\u00f3rico da vila e zonas industriais adjacentes. A organiza\u00e7\u00e3o utiliza sinal\u00e9tica crom\u00e1tica espec\u00edfica para cada esta\u00e7\u00e3o, sendo o verde a cor predominante nesta edi\u00e7\u00e3o de primavera para identificar os postos de cronometragem. <sup><\/sup><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\ud83c\udf0d <strong>Sobre o Local:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Situada na transi\u00e7\u00e3o entre o Maci\u00e7o Calc\u00e1rio Estremenho e as Serras da Lous\u00e3, a vila de Avelar oferece um cen\u00e1rio de encostas suaves. Para a reposi\u00e7\u00e3o nutricional ap\u00f3s a prova, recomenda-se o <strong>Queijo do Raba\u00e7al<\/strong> (DOP), acompanhado pelo p\u00e3o de trigo local, fornecendo o equil\u00edbrio necess\u00e1rio entre hidratos de carbono e prote\u00ednas de alta qualidade.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":50342,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"zakra_general_container_width":0,"zakra_general_content_width":0,"zakra_general_sidebar_width":0,"zakra_sticky_header":"customizer","zakra_header_main_area":true,"zakra_site_logo_width":0,"zakra_header_top_enabled":"customizer","zakra_header_top_style":"customizer","zakra_primary_menu_item_style":"customizer","zakra_page_header_text_color":"","zakra_page_header_layout":"customizer","zakra_page_title_bg":"","zakra_footer_widgets_bg_image":0,"zakra_page_title_bg_repeat":"customizer","zakra_page_title_bg_position":"customizer","zakra_page_title_bg_size":"customizer","zakra_page_title_bg_attachment":"customizer","zakra_breadcrumbs_enabled":"customizer","zakra_breadcrumbs_text_color":"","zakra_breadcrumbs_separator_color":"","zakra_breadcrumbs_link_color":"","zakra_breadcrumbs_link_hover_color":"","zakra_page_title_bg_image":0,"zakra_footer_widgets_enabled":"customizer","zakra_footer_column_layout_1_style":"customizer","zakra_footer_widgets_bg":"","zakra_footer_widgets_bg_repeat":"customizer","zakra_footer_widgets_bg_position":"customizer","zakra_footer_widgets_bg_size":"customizer","zakra_footer_widgets_bg_attachment":"customizer","zakra_